    "content": "<p>The equivalent resistance of the circuit across $A B$ is given by</p>\n<p><img alt=\"BITSAT 2025 Physics - Semiconductor Devices and Logic Gates Question 1 English\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mnqh2qgv/561d3e27-11ef-4dfc-b95c-c66bd40268b4/897550f0-3385-11f1-9cee-13299b95b990/file-jaoe38c1mnqh2qgw.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mnqh2qgv/561d3e27-11ef-4dfc-b95c-c66bd40268b4/897550f0-3385-11f1-9cee-13299b95b990/file-jaoe38c1mnqh2qgw.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>",
    "options": [
