    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lx415co7/de0ae7dd-7915-4e86-8847-8a639b02cc6f/6205f770-2470-11ef-ade3-4f3c90942dca/file-jaoe38c1lx415co8.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lx415co7/de0ae7dd-7915-4e86-8847-8a639b02cc6f/6205f770-2470-11ef-ade3-4f3c90942dca/file-jaoe38c1lx415co8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"BITSAT 2023 Physics - Semiconductor Devices and Logic Gates Question 4 English Explanation 1\"></p>\n<p>$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n\\therefore Y &amp; =\\overline{\\overline{(\\bar{A} \\cdot \\overline{A B}})(\\bar{B} \\cdot \\overline{A B})} \\\\\n&amp; \\overline{A \\cdot \\overline{A B}}+\\overline{B \\cdot \\overline{A B}} \\\\\n&amp; =\\bar{A}+A B+\\bar{B}+A B \\\\\n&amp; =\\overline{A B}+A B=1\n\\end{aligned}$$</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1lx414oek/a4ce981c-24ae-47c6-8727-9c4519e63d5b/4f46ecc0-2470-11ef-ade3-4f3c90942dca/file-jaoe38c1lx414oel.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1lx414oek/a4ce981c-24ae-47c6-8727-9c4519e63d5b/4f46ecc0-2470-11ef-ade3-4f3c90942dca/file-jaoe38c1lx414oel.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"BITSAT 2023 Physics - Semiconductor Devices and Logic Gates Question 4 English Explanation 2\"></p>",
