    "content": "<p>The combination of the gates shown in following figure yields</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/6y3zli1ls1lo5d9/8ce84d62-0d44-4556-95ab-ad42be4c2524/347ebdd0-c01d-11ee-a44e-4fd06148d0b3/file-6y3zli1ls1lo5da.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/6y3zli1ls1lo5d9/8ce84d62-0d44-4556-95ab-ad42be4c2524/347ebdd0-c01d-11ee-a44e-4fd06148d0b3/file-6y3zli1ls1lo5da.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"BITSAT 2020 Physics - Semiconductor Devices and Logic Gates Question 10 English\"></p>",
